+  // browser-view / windows / dialogs / JSON-RPC fanout hosts.
+  //
+  // cap-shell-3 — TerminalHost: unlike the other four, each JS
+  // `TerminalHost.getRemote()` spawns a fresh SlayzoneTerminalHost (one pty
